trans-unit.target: TEXT_REGLAKMASTERGATHERER_00161_TATAROGA_000_000<tab>I'm a personal assistant of Master Wiscard hisself. Who're you? You don't know the big man? Then, all the 'stounding wares I have─you don't know these either. Farewell!
TEXT_REGLAKMASTERGATHERER_00161_TATAROGA_000_010<tab>You know Master Wiscard? Why didn't you say so!? Come on in, you'll find something in here for you!
